{"id":3109,"date":"2016-04-09T17:35:57","date_gmt":"2016-04-09T17:35:57","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/twelvershia.net\/?p=3109"},"modified":"2017-02-16T21:27:17","modified_gmt":"2017-02-16T21:27:17","slug":"response-to-abu-bakars-first-speech","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2016\/04\/09\/response-to-abu-bakars-first-speech\/","title":{"rendered":"Response to: Abu bakar\u2019s first speech &#038; quran"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/imgstore.org\/a\/67hxw0egsgub?i=3109\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The following is a response to Slave of Ahlubait\u2019s \u201cAbu bakar\u2019s first speech &amp; quran\u201d. The article can be found in <a href=\"https:\/\/ahlubait.wordpress.com\/2010\/02\/06\/abu-bakars-first-speech-quran\/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">his blog<\/a> and the <a href=\"http:\/\/wilayat.net\/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2250:abu-bakar&amp;rsquo;s-first-speech-quran=&amp;catid=174:abu-bakr-1st-caliph&amp;lang=en&amp;Itemid=108\" rel=\"external nofollow\">wilayat website.<\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The article contains a speech by Abu Bakr which contains the following:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\">\u201c<em>Lo! Indeed the <\/em><em>Shaitan<\/em><em> attacks me. So when he comes to me, stay away from me.\u201d<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Slave of Ahlubait then quotes the verse:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">And whoever turns himself away from the remembrance of the Beneficent Allah, We appoint for him a Shaitan, so he becomes his associate \u2013 Al-Zukhruf : 36<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Without even going into the meaning of the verse and Abu Bakr\u2019s intentions with these words, we simply point to the fact that this narration comes from the path of Saif bin Omar Al-Tameemi.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Slave of Ahlubait <a href=\"https:\/\/ahlubait.wordpress.com\/2010\/08\/26\/prophet-asws-curses-mawia-sunnis-scholars-hide-the-name\/\" rel=\"external nofollow\">admits in another article<\/a> that the man is a liar.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">His exact words are:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\">\u201che mentioned chain of famous liar, saif bin umar tameemi<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #800000;\"> the one on whom syed murtaza askari wrote book even;\u201d<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is no need to add anymore to this refutation.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<div class=\"mh-excerpt\"><p>The following is a response to Slave of Ahlubait\u2019s \u201cAbu bakar\u2019s first speech &amp; quran\u201d. The article can be found in his blog and the wilayat website. The article contains a speech by Abu Bakr which contains the following: \u201cLo! <a class=\"mh-excerpt-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/2016\/04\/09\/response-to-abu-bakars-first-speech\/\" title=\"Response to: Abu bakar\u2019s first speech &#038; quran\">[read more]<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":3894,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11],"tags":[17],"class_list":{"0":"post-3109","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-articles","8":"tag-abu-bakr"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3109","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.twelvershia.net\/wp-json\/wp\